latestIgtvVideos.title: Happy Mother's Day
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Well my mom is a warrior. She is my greatest inspiration. She despite of being a work oriented woman, handles my whole big family of TEN members in it. She takes care of everything that each one of us needs. The whole family is proud of her😇.
Thank you for everything maa. Thank you for doing so much for the whole family. Thank you for the sacrifices you have made. Thank you for always standing strong no matter what.

latestIgtvVideos.title: KUDI NU NACHNE DE with my SQUAD❤
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Well even we tried to follow the trend of making covers of the song KUDI NU NACHNE DE. Moreover we just wanted to make a memory of all FIVE of us. Please do not judge our moves😄.. not pro dancers though. But we really enjoyed making this. I have been asking them to send their videos since almost a week now and today I managed to get them finally. My girls are quite busy even during lockdown you know🙄. Soooo yeah here it is. Celebrating womenhood and our 9 years of friendship. 🧡

latestPosts.caption:
Living my childhood dream of decorating my own home for Bihu, just the way little me always imagined.

Bihu decor, rongali bihu, Assamese decor, home decor

First Bihu as Parents 🧿🫶
This Bihu feels so different. I miss seeing him the way I used to… as my husband, my partner in every little celebration, my fun person . But nowadays, I mostly see him in a new role as a father. And while that fills my heart with a new kind of happiness, a quiet part of me still aches for the man who was just mine and the US we were.
This Bihu, we celebrate not just a festival, but a new beginning. New roles, new routines, and a whole new kind of love. Happy Bihu from our growing little world to yours.
